casebody.data:
Drummond v. Fisher. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

May 12, 1892.) Action by Robert W. Drummond against Frank L. Fisher.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bischoff, JJ.

Ho opinion. Motion for leave to appeal to the court of appeals denied, with $10 costs. See 16 N. Y. Supp. 867; 18 N. Y. Supp. 142.
